high_descs: Turn around, walk halfway across the room and then turn left to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the right and face the tomato on the counter.
cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Take a step to the left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the pan with the knife in it on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Step to the left and focus on the pan on the counter.
Put the tomato slice in the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To cut a tomato as well as putting the tomato slice and a knife in a pan plus sitting it on the counter.

high_descs: go the counter between the fridge and stove
pick up the knife from the counter
take a few steps to the right
slice the tomato
walk the knife over the stove
put the knife in the pan on the back right burner of the stove
pick up the pan with the knife in it
take pan and knife back to counter with tomato slices
put the pan and knife on the counter
take few steps to the right
Pick up one tomato slice
take a few steps back to the left
Put the tomato slice in the pan with the knife
anns.task_desc: Cut a tomato and put one slice in a pan

high_descs: Move to the counter between the refrigerator and stove.
Pick up the knife that is near the fork.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the tomato.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Turn to the right, move to in front of the stove.
Place the knife into the pan that is on the right.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left, move to the counter to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the pan on to the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the pan.
Put the tomato slice in to the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato in a pan.

high_descs: Turn around, walk across the room, past the refrigerator, and turn to your left, facing the first kitchen counter top before the stove.
Grab the butter knife that is on the counter, between the fork and the lettuce.
Move over to your right so that you are right in front of the tomato near the edge of the counter.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Move over to your right again so that you are in standing directly in front of the oven.
Place the knife in the fry pan that is on the rear, right side of the stove top.
Pick up the fry pan with the knife inside.
Move over to your left so that you are directly in front of the kitchen counter with the sliced tomato on it.
Set the fry pan with the knife inside it on the counter, beside the tomato.
Move to your right so that you are once again directly in front of the tomato.
Pick up one of the tomato slices previously cut.
Move to your left so that you are directly in front of the fry pan.
Place the tomato slice in the fry pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice into a fry pan.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter next to the stove to your left.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the tomato on the counter on your left.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the stove to your left.
Place the knife in the right pot on the stove.
Take the pot with the knife from the stove in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter on your right.
Place the pot with knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter by the stove on your right.
Place the tomato slice on the pot on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice in a pot.

high_descs: turn right and head for the gas
pick up a knife at the left of the gas
move right towards the tomato on the table
slice the tomato with the knife
move right towards the gas
place the knife on the pan on the gas
pick up the pan
head for the left side of the gas
drop the pan on  the left side of the gas
move to the right side of the gas
pick up a slice of the tomato
move left towards the  pan
drop the tomato slice in the pan
anns.task_desc: drop a tomato slice with a knife inside a pan
